<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" />
</head>

<style>
  #camino li {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-top: 3px;
    padding-left: 1em;
    text-indent: -0.7em;
    margin: 0 0 3px 0;
  }
  #camino li:before {
    content: "• ";
    color: darkred;
  }
</style>

<section>
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-accent mb-6 pt-8 italic">
      <%= title "Aikku PROJECTS" %>
    </h1>
    <h2 class="text-lg xl:text-2xl px-6">
      <%= description "Manage your projects, as a team and mobility" %>
    </h2>
  </div>
</section>

  <div id="carousel" class="carousel min-w-16 sm:w-3/4 mx-auto shadow-lg">
    <div id="slide1" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/projets.png" %>
    </div> 
    <div id="slide2" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/projet.png" %>
    </div> 
    <div id="slide3" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/todolist.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide4" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/todo.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide5" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/agenda.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide6" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/documents.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide7" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/tables.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide8" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/dashboard.png" %>
    </div>
    <div id="slide9" class="carousel-item relative w-full">
      <%= image_tag "camino/user.png" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-controller="carousel-paginate">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center w-full gap-2 mt-4">
      <a href="#slide1" class="btn btn-accent hover:btn-accent btn-xs carousel-page" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">1</a> 
      <a href="#slide2" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">2</a> 
      <a href="#slide3" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">3</a> 
      <a href="#slide4" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">4</a> 
      <a href="#slide5" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">5</a> 
      <a href="#slide6" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">6</a> 
      <a href="#slide7" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">7</a> 
      <a href="#slide8" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">8</a> 
      <a href="#slide9" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline btn-xs carousel-page hover:btn-accent" data-action="click->carousel-paginate#activate">9</a> 
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="px-8 mt-12">
  <div id="camino" class="text-xl">

    <h3 class="apps-title">
      Manage your projects, as a team and mobility (follow -up of interventions, GMAO, etc ...)
    </h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Cut your projects into lists of things to do</li>
      <li>Invite your contacts to participate in projects</li>
      <li>Assign things to do to the participants, set deadlines</li>
      <li>Follow the activity of the participants by subscribing to the notifications (completed work, new comments, addition/modification ...)</li>
      <li>Create forms to collect additional data to your projects (inventory, intervention report, etc.)</li>
    </ul>


    <h3 class="apps-title">Features</h3>
    <div>
      <ul>
        <li>Quick creation of projects from your <b> Project models</b></li>
        <li>Choice of <b> workflow </b> (type of project course, free or linear) </li>
        <li>A <b> journal </b> lists, minute per minute, the activity of the participants.All changes are recorded </li>
        <li>An <b> agenda </b> allows you to visualize the global deadlines </li>
        <li>The <b> 'to-do' </b> list, pending, suffering or made by participant </b>
        <li>Participants can conduct <b> discussions </b> around things to do </li>
        <li>A <b> notification system </b> by email informs the participants of the project </li>
        <li> Regrouping of projects by <b> Keywords </b> </li>
        <li>A <b> color </b> for each project in order to better identify the information relating to it </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="apps-title">Forms and data tables</h3>
    <p>
      Create your own forms to collect additional information to your projects (time spent, resources consumed, intervention reports, etc.).
The data is collected in data tables that you can then export to Excel.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-5">
    To find out more, please consult
    <%= link_to "The user guide", 'https://projects.aikku.eu/about', class: 'link', target: '_blank' %>
  </p>

  <h3 class="apps-title">Demonstration</h3>
  <p>
    Want to test the product?
    <%= link_to "Launch the demonstration body", 'https://projects.aikku.eu', class:'link', target: '_blank' %>
  </p>

  <h3 class="apps-title">Development</h3>
  <p>
    Aikku PROJECTS is developed and maintained by
    <%= link_to 'AIKKU SAS', root_path, class: 'link' %>
  </p>

  <h3 class="apps-title">Support and services</h3>
  <p>
    Do you want a new feature or install Aikku PROJECTS on your Linux server?
    <%= link_to 'Consult our service offer', '/services', class: 'link' %>
  </p>
</div>